{"tid":2149071,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"壹週刊：2020年8月10日，你還覺得新聞自由是必然的嗎？","createTime":"2020-08-10T08:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T08:30:28.000Z","uid":14730,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ee0ff39b72a58aa61e93ed8dbcd20ffbcdfc38f8","tid":2149071,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:23:12.000Z","msg":"課金！訂閱！<br />\n還未訂閱《壹週刊》的香港人，請按此立即訂閱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmag.hk/e/NXeKVODrVZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmag.hk%2Fe%2FNXeKVODrVZ&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=d03384b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmag.hk/e/NXeKVODrVZ</a> <br />\n如欲進一步撐《壹週刊》，請按此支持「和你撐壹週刊」計劃：<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmag.hk/e/qvtlf3GXn7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmag.hk%2Fe%2Fqvtlf3GXn7&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=516a74d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmag.hk/e/qvtlf3GXn7</a> <br />\n如欲為身邊人訂閱《壹週刊》，請按此購買贈閱劵：<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmag.hk/e/3DCMTtOQr6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmag.hk%2Fe%2F3DCMTtOQr6&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=ff22c879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmag.hk/e/3DCMTtOQr6</a><br />\n<br />\n今天早上，壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英，被登門拘捕了，罪名是：涉嫌勾結外國勢力。<br />\n為了壹傳媒可以多撐一天得一天，黎智英早前曾在鏡頭前坦承「我們經營困難」，然而，經營一個為講真相，處處和政權對着幹的傳媒，何只困難？<br />\n昔日戰友變節了，黎智英說不要緊；廣告客戶走光了，黎智英說試試行訂閱制吧，我們將真相放在 Paywall後面，不只是因為「新聞有價」，這一舉，也是為了集合志同道合的真香港人，一起看清真相、了解真相，並且成為我們的壹分子，一同聚集力量、宣揚真相。<br />\n訂閱制為《壹週刊》創造了奇蹟，近十萬位付費訂戶用行動告訴壹仔，必須繼續踢爆勾結、繼續揭發黑幕。<br />\n來到這一刻，我們會退縮嗎？<br />\n前路很顛簸，但，作為新聞工作者、作為香港人，我們心裡明白，以後日子再明哲保身也沒用。<br />\n請讓我代黎智英先生作出一次存亡號召，自己傳媒自己撐，請訂閱《壹週刊》，支持我們的工作，也讓我們的聲音，成為一棵不倒的稻草。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_753833_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_753833_0&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=aa85593a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_753833_0&h=8d27e2d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_753833_0</a>"},{"pid":"f3f9717967d5711c01278083f2b5672c8603ee8d","tid":2149071,"uid":14730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:23:59.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"5062ef67ec06c5f11ae1df576fcc031d4f243362","tid":2149071,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12d8144df209353c23eb10b39d12bc0632c38ea7","tid":2149071,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:24:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"087a5810fabd8a6078d69bd40f9d74f25bff9b34","tid":2149071,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:24:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd46884676b6f7e1470f692cd9f024371122e9c5","tid":2149071,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:24:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f92b6ff428cd5b0d0dd71dd5d7d863b8e8ca13b5","tid":2149071,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:24:46.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c8f963ca51b510835a752a3abb35558d1a9027","tid":2149071,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"課完再課<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fc2ae9ff7f76f116285a37a17e0bbf943f7c9b","tid":2149071,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595b3303377a8bb7a4b13f24800c24d9da653b4f","tid":2149071,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0